# Installation instructions:
# 1. Install system dependencies:
#    - Windows: No additional system dependencies needed
#    - Linux: sudo apt-get install python3-dev
#    - macOS: No additional system dependencies needed
#
# 2. Install Python packages:
#    pip install -r analytics_requirements.txt
#
# 3. For Redis (if using Celery):
#    - Windows: Download and install Redis
#    - Linux: sudo apt-get install redis-server
#    - macOS: brew install redis
#
# 4. Optional ML packages (large downloads):
#    pip install tensorflow  # For advanced ML features
#    pip install torch       # For advanced ML features
#
# 5. Environment variables (optional):
#    - ANALYTICS_DB_PATH=/path/to/analytics.db
